quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"We sent it down on the Night of Determination.",footnotes:366520:1
  97,2,"But what can make yousg realize what the Night of Determination is?"
  97,3,"The Night of Determination is better than a thousand months—"
  97,4,"in it descend the angels, with the Spirit among them, by the leave of their Lord with every command.",footnotes:366521:1
  97,5,"Peace! It is until the rise of dawn.",footnotes:366522:1
